      <p></p>
<p>As you embark on this incredible journey of parenthood, know that you're surrounded by love and support.  These messages are crafted to express the deep joy and excitement we feel for you both.</p>
<li>Wishing you a lifetime of love, laughter, and tiny toes.</li>
<li>Congratulations on your precious bundle of joy!</li>
<li>May your days be filled with the sweetest of lullabies.</li>
<li>Sending you all our love as you prepare for this beautiful chapter.</li>
<li>May your parenthood journey be filled with unforgettable moments.</li>
<li>So excited to welcome your little one into the world!</li>
<li>Wishing you both a smooth and happy pregnancy.</li>
<li>Congratulations on creating a family filled with love.</li>
<li>May your hearts overflow with joy as you meet your baby.</li>
<li>Here’s to sleepless nights and endless love.</li>
<li>We're so happy to share in your excitement!</li>
<li>Wishing you all the best as you prepare for this incredible adventure.</li>
<li>May your home be filled with the sound of sweet giggles.</li>
<li>Congratulations on the wonderful news! We can't wait to meet the little one.</li>
<li>Embrace this beautiful journey; parenthood is a remarkable gift.</li>
    

